        CHANGES IN spagmix VERSION 0.3-2

OVERVIEW

    o Fixed offset scaling issue in 'lgcpmix'



        CHANGES IN spagmix VERSION 0.3-1

OVERVIEW

    o Removed 'MCMCpack' import designation; required functionality now in-built
    o Internal functions added
    o R version requirement bumped up to 3.5.0



        CHANGES IN spagmix VERSION 0.3-0

OVERVIEW

    o New functionality for generating realisations of inhomogeneous spatial log-Gaussian Cox process intensities


NEW FUNCTIONS

    o lgcpmix
    Inhomogeneous log-Gaussian Cox process intensity generator (spatial only)
    o rpoispoly
    Generate a random realisation of a Poisson point process to fall inside a polygonal window given a spatial intensity pixel image


SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o spagmix now imports the RandomFields package



